Eroarea:   SELECT X."IdRol", X."RolDenumire" FROM (SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) AS int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE C."IdSuper" = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) as int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE J."IdUser" = ) X 
                                WHERE X.F10022 <= '2021-08-31' AND '2021-08-01' <= X.F10023
                                GROUP BY X."IdRol", X."RolDenumire"
                                ORDER BY X."IdRol" DESC

                                LEFT JOIN "tblMeniuri" E ON E."Id" = B."IdNomen"
                                WHERE D."IdUser" = @1 AND B."Stare" = 1
                                GROUP BY B."Parinte", B."IdMeniu", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                ORDER BY B."Parinte", B."Ordine"

                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) AS int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506

                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE C."IdSuper" = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) as int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506

                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE J."IdUser" = ) X 
                                WHERE X.F10022 <= '2021-09-30' AND '2021-09-01' <= X.F10023
                                GROUP BY X."IdRol", X."RolDenumire"
                                ORDER BY X."IdRol" DESC

Eroarea:   SELECT B."IdMeniu", B."Parinte", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                FROM "MeniuLinii" B
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupMeniu2" C ON B."IdMeniu" = C."IdMeniu"
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" D ON C."IdGrup" = D."IdGrup"
                                LEFT JOIN "tblMeniuri" E ON E."Id" = B."IdNomen"

                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia",

                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506

                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) as int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202

                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405

                                WHERE J."IdUser" = ) X 
                                WHERE X.F10022 <= '2021-09-30' AND '2021-09-01' <= X.F10023
                                GROUP BY X."IdRol", X."RolDenumire"
                                ORDER BY X."IdRol" DESC

Eveni:     IncarcaDT
Eroarea:   SELECT B."IdMeniu", B."Parinte", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                FROM "MeniuLinii" B
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupMeniu2" C ON B."IdMeniu" = C."IdMeniu"
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" D ON C."IdGrup" = D."IdGrup"
                                LEFT JOIN "tblMeniuri" E ON E."Id" = B."IdNomen"
                                WHERE D."IdUser" = @1 AND B."Stare" = 1
                                GROUP BY B."Parinte", B."IdMeniu", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                ORDER BY B."Parinte", B."Ordine"

Eroarea:   SELECT B."IdMeniu", B."Parinte", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                FROM "MeniuLinii" B
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupMeniu2" C ON B."IdMeniu" = C."IdMeniu"
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" D ON C."IdGrup" = D."IdGrup"
                                LEFT JOIN "tblMeniuri" E ON E."Id" = B."IdNomen"
                                WHERE D."IdUser" = @1 AND B."Stare" = 1
                                GROUP BY B."Parinte", B."IdMeniu", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                ORDER BY B."Parinte", B."Ordine"

Eroarea:   SELECT X."IdRol", X."RolDenumire" FROM (SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) AS int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE C."IdSuper" = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) as int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE J."IdUser" = ) X 
                                WHERE X.F10022 <= '2021-09-30' AND '2021-09-01' <= X.F10023
                                GROUP BY X."IdRol", X."RolDenumire"
                                ORDER BY X."IdRol" DESC

                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE C."IdSuper" = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) as int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE J."IdUser" = ) X 
                            WHERE X."IdRol" = -99 AND X.F10022 <= '2021-09-30' AND '2021-09-01' <= X.F10023
                            ORDER BY X."NumeComplet"

Data:    07.09.2021 08:27:09
Pagina:    General
Eveni:     IncarcaDT
Eroarea:   SELECT B."IdMeniu", B."Parinte", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                FROM "MeniuLinii" B
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupMeniu2" C ON B."IdMeniu" = C."IdMeniu"
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" D ON C."IdGrup" = D."IdGrup"
                                LEFT JOIN "tblMeniuri" E ON E."Id" = B."IdNomen"
                                WHERE D."IdUser" = @1 AND B."Stare" = 1
                                GROUP BY B."Parinte", B."IdMeniu", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                ORDER BY B."Parinte", B."Ordine"

Eroarea:   SELECT B."IdMeniu", B."Parinte", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"

                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) AS int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025

                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506

                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) as int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802

                                WHERE X.F10022 <= '2021-09-30' AND '2021-09-01' <= X.F10023
                                GROUP BY X."IdRol", X."RolDenumire"
                                ORDER BY X."IdRol" DESC

                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE C."IdSuper" = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) as int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE J."IdUser" = ) X 
                            WHERE X."IdRol" = -99 AND X.F10022 <= '2021-09-30' AND '2021-09-01' <= X.F10023
                            ORDER BY X."NumeComplet"

                                GROUP BY B."Parinte", B."IdMeniu", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"

Eroarea:   SELECT B."IdMeniu", B."Parinte", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                FROM "MeniuLinii" B
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupMeniu2" C ON B."IdMeniu" = C."IdMeniu"
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" D ON C."IdGrup" = D."IdGrup"
                                LEFT JOIN "tblMeniuri" E ON E."Id" = B."IdNomen"

                                GROUP BY B."Parinte", B."IdMeniu", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"

Eveni:     IncarcaDT
Eroarea:   SELECT B."IdMeniu", B."Parinte", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                FROM "MeniuLinii" B
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupMeniu2" C ON B."IdMeniu" = C."IdMeniu"
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" D ON C."IdGrup" = D."IdGrup"
                                LEFT JOIN "tblMeniuri" E ON E."Id" = B."IdNomen"
                                WHERE D."IdUser" = @1 AND B."Stare" = 1
                                GROUP BY B."Parinte", B."IdMeniu", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                ORDER BY B."Parinte", B."Ordine"

Eroarea:   SELECT X."IdRol", X."RolDenumire" FROM (SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) AS int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE C."IdSuper" = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) as int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE J."IdUser" = ) X 
                                WHERE X.F10022 <= '2021-09-30' AND '2021-09-01' <= X.F10023
                                GROUP BY X."IdRol", X."RolDenumire"
                                ORDER BY X."IdRol" DESC

                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) AS int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304

                                WHERE C."IdSuper" =

                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) as int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304

                        INNER JOIN "Ptj_Circuit" C ON B."IdSuper" = -1 * c."UserIntrod" 
                        LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" D ON D."Id" = B."IdSuper"
                        WHERE B."IdUser"= 
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, 76 AS "Rol", 'Fara rol' AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "Ptj_Circuit" C ON C."UserIntrod"= ) B
                        INNER JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN F718 X ON A.F10071=X.F71802
                        LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                        LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                        LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                        LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                        WHERE 1=1

                    CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" =  AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <>    and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser= and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                        FROM F100 A

RefuseReason,  (CASE WHEN av.TotalAmount IS NULL THEN dec.TotalAmount ELSE av.TotalAmount END) AS TotalAmountDocument,  (CASE WHEN av.CurrencyId IS NULL THEN dec.CurrencyId ELSE av.CurrencyId END) AS CurrencyIdDocument,  (CASE WHEN avMoneda.DictionaryItemName IS NULL THEN decMoneda.DictionaryItemName ELSE avMoneda.DictionaryItemName END) AS CurrencyCodeDocument,  (CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN ELSE bugOwner.DocumentTypeId END )  AND (CASE WHEN docState.IdSuper IS NULL THEN -99 ELSE docState.IdSuper END) =  (CASE WHEN bugOwner.IdSuper IS NULL THEN -99 ELSE bugOwner.IdSuper END)  WHERE Eveni:     IncarcaDT
Eroarea:   SELECT a.DocumentId, b.DocumentTypeName, a.DocumentTypeId, a.F10003, a.DocumentDate, c.F10008 + ' ' + c.F10009 AS NumeComplet,  d.DictionaryItemName AS Stare, a.DocumentStateId AS IdStare, a.Culoare, a.TIME, a.CircuitId AS IdCircuit, a.USER_NO, srcDoc.SrcDocId,  (CASE WHEN av.RefuseReason IS NULL OR LEN(av.RefuseReason) <= 0 THEN dec.RefuseReason ELSE av.RefuseReason END) AS RefuseReason,  (CASE WHEN av.TotalAmount IS NULL THEN dec.TotalAmount ELSE av.TotalAmount END) AS TotalAmountDocument,  (CASE WHEN av.CurrencyId IS NULL THEN dec.CurrencyId ELSE av.CurrencyId END) AS CurrencyIdDocument,  (CASE WHEN avMoneda.DictionaryItemName IS NULL THEN decMoneda.DictionaryItemName ELSE avMoneda.DictionaryItemName END) AS CurrencyCodeDocument,  (CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN bugOwner.IdSuper IS NULL THEN -99 ELSE bugOwner.IdSuper END) = -99 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) AS IsBudgetOwnerForDocument,  (CASE WHEN (a.DocumentTypeId IN (1001, 1002, 1003, 1004) AND a.DocumentStateId < 4 AND a.USER_NO != docState.USER_NO) OR  (a.DocumentTypeId IN (2001, 2002, 2003) AND a.DocumentStateId < 7 AND a.USER_NO != docState.USER_NO)  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS canBeRefused, a.Pozitie  FROM AvsXDec_Document a  JOIN AvsXDec_DocumentStateHistory docState ON a.DocumentId = docState.DocumentId  JOIN AvsXDec_DocumentType b on a.DocumentTypeId = b.DocumentTypeId  JOIN F100 c on a.F10003 = c.F10003  JOIN vwAvsXDec_Nomen_StariDoc d on a.DocumentStateId = d.DictionaryItemId  LEFT JOIN AvsXDec_BusinessTransaction srcDoc on a.DocumentId = srcDoc.DestDocId  LEFT JOIN AvsXDec_Avans av on a.DocumentId = av.DocumentId  LEFT JOIN vwAvsXDec_Nomen_TipMoneda avMoneda on av.CurrencyId = avMoneda.DictionaryItemId  LEFT JOIN AvsXDec_Decont dec on a.DocumentId = dec.DocumentId  LEFT JOIN vwAvsXDec_Nomen_TipMoneda decMoneda on dec.CurrencyId = decMoneda.DictionaryItemId  LEFT JOIN vwAvsXDec_BudgetOwner bugOwner on  a.DocumentTypeId = (CASE WHEN bugOwner.DocumentTypeId IS NULL THEN -99 ELSE bugOwner.DocumentTypeId END )  AND (CASE WHEN docState.IdSuper IS NULL THEN -99 ELSE docState.IdSuper END) =  (CASE WHEN bugOwner.IdSuper IS NULL THEN -99 ELSE bugOwner.IdSuper END)  WHERE (docState.USER_NO = 3	OR docState.IdUserInlocuitor = 3)

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra6" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra6" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra6")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=6) + '=' + "CampExtra6" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra7" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra7" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra7")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=7) + '=' + "CampExtra7" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra8" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra8" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra8")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=8) + '=' + "CampExtra8" + '; ' ELSE '' END +

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra10" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra10" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra10")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=10) + '=' + "CampExtra10" + '; ' ELSE '' END +

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra12" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra12" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra12")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=12) + '=' + "CampExtra12" + '; ' ELSE '' END +

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra14" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra14" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra14")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=14) + '=' + "CampExtra14" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra15" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra15" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra15")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=15) + '=' + "CampExtra15" + '; ' ELSE '' END +

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra17")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=17) + '=' + "CampExtra17" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra18")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=18) + '=' + "CampExtra18" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra19")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=19) + '=' + "CampExtra19" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra20")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=20) + '=' + "CampExtra20" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                    CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 25 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 22254
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 25
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> 22254   and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser=25 and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=25 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-10-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra1" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra1" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra1")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=1) + '=' + "CampExtra1" + '; ' ELSE '' END +

                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 25 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 22254
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 25

                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=25 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-01-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 25 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 22254
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 25
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> 22254   and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser=25 and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=25 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-01-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-01-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN

                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=25 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-01-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 25
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> 22254   and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser=25 and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=25 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-01-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 25 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 22254
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 25
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> 22254   and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser=25 and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=25 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-01-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra17")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=17) + '=' + "CampExtra17" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra18")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=18) + '=' + "CampExtra18" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra19")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=19) + '=' + "CampExtra19" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra20")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=20) + '=' + "CampExtra20" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                    CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 25 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 22254
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 25
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> 22254   and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser=25 and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=25 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-10-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

Eroarea:   SELECT "Rol" AS "Id", "RolDenumire" AS "Denumire" FROM (
                            SELECT "Rol", "RolDenumire", 1 AS "Ordin" FROM (SELECT A."Id", B.F10003, B.F10008 + ' ' + B.F10009 AS "NumeAngajat", F00305 AS Subcompania, A."IdAbsenta", A."DataInceput", A."DataSfarsit", B.F100901 AS EID,
                                CASE WHEN E."Alias" IS NULL OR E."Alias"='' THEN E."Denumire" ELSE E."Alias" END AS "RolDenumire",
                                A."Rol", A."Actiune", A."Inlocuitor", COALESCE(C."AdaugaAtasament",0) AS "AdaugaAtasament",
                                A."NrZile" AS "NrZile", 
                                CASE WHEN C."IdTipOre" = 0 THEN A."NrOre" ELSE NULL END AS "NrOre", 
                                A."Observatii", D.F10008 + ' ' + D.F10009 AS "NumeInlocuitor", A."IdStare", 
                                CASE WHEN A."TrimiteLa" = -13 THEN 'Banca' ELSE CASE WHEN A."TrimiteLa"= -14 THEN 'Plata' ELSE Q."Denumire" END END AS "TrimiteLa",

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra19")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=19) + '=' + "CampExtra19" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra20")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=20) + '=' + "CampExtra20" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                    CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 25 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 22254
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 25
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> 22254   and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser=25 and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=25 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-10-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

AND a.USER_NO != docState.USER_NO) OR  (a.DocumentTypeId IN (2001, 2002, 2003) AND a.DocumentStateId < 7 AND a.USER_NO != docState.USER_NO)  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS canBeRefused, a.Pozitie  FROM c.F10003  JOIN vwAvsXDec_Nomen_StariDoc d on a.DocumentStateId = d.DictionaryItemId  LEFT JOIN AvsXDec_BusinessTransaction srcDoc on a.DocumentId = srcDoc.DestDocId  LEFT JOIN AvsXDec_Avans av on a.DocumentId = av.DocumentId  LEFT JOIN vwAvsXDec_Nomen_TipMoneda avMoneda on av.CurrencyId = avMoneda.DictionaryItemId  LEFT JOIN AvsXDec_Decont dec on a.DocumentId = dec.DocumentId  LEFT JOIN vwAvsXDec_Nomen_TipMoneda decMoneda on dec.CurrencyId = decMoneda.DictionaryItemId  LEFT JOIN vwAvsXDec_BudgetOwner bugOwner on  a.DocumentTypeId = (CASE WHEN bugOwner.DocumentTypeId IS NULL THEN -99 ELSE bugOwner.DocumentTypeId END )  AND (CASE WHEN docState.IdSuper IS NULL THEN -99 ELSE docState.IdSuper END) =  (CASE WHEN bugOwner.IdSuper IS NULL THEN -99 ELSE bugOwner.IdSuper END)  WHERE RefuseReason,  (CASE WHEN av.TotalAmount IS NULL THEN dec.TotalAmount ELSE av.TotalAmount END) AS TotalAmountDocument,  (CASE WHEN av.CurrencyId IS NULL THEN dec.CurrencyId ELSE av.CurrencyId END) AS CurrencyIdDocument,  (CASE WHEN avMoneda.DictionaryItemName IS NULL THEN decMoneda.DictionaryItemName ELSE avMoneda.DictionaryItemName END) AS CurrencyCodeDocument,  (CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN c.F10003  JOIN vwAvsXDec_Nomen_StariDoc d on a.DocumentStateId = d.DictionaryItemId  LEFT JOIN AvsXDec_BusinessTransaction srcDoc on a.DocumentId = srcDoc.DestDocId  LEFT JOIN AvsXDec_Avans av on Eroarea:   SELECT X."IdRol", X."RolDenumire" FROM (SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) AS int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE C."IdSuper" = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) as int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE J."IdUser" = ) X 
                                
                                GROUP BY X."IdRol", X."RolDenumire"
                                ORDER BY X."IdRol" DESC

                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) AS int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(S."Denumire", '') AS "RolDenumire", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblRoluri" S ON C."IdRol"=S."Id"
                                WHERE C."IdSuper" = {0}
                                UNION
                                SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 {1} ' ' {1} a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie",

                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802

                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304

                                UNION
